{"title":"大跃进中的小插曲","authors":["张永枚"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大跃进中的小插曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4000万吨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个光辉的数目字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已在我们心中生根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要在十五年内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"达到每年产钢4000万吨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呀！4000万吨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕会忘掉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱人在哪年哪月出生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——可以再问问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不能忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4000万吨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们炼钢工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是钢的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用劳动抚育"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个坚强的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——4000万吨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面前是灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里是针"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪刀嚓嚓响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜已三更"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件破旧的大衣剪裁了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件翻新的短袄改缝成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的剪刀真锋利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪掉了浪费的坏思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的针线真巧妙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝起了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤俭持家的好家声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永枚"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}